nodes.text: Dean Kiner is a music composer who worked on Star Wars Rebels and on the seventh season of Star Wars: The Clone Wars. The son of Kevin Kiner—a composer who worked on both the Rebels and Star Wars: The Clone Wars television series—he and his brother, Sean, wrote music alongide their father for the Star Wars series. He gratuated from Berklee College of Music and plays for his band Illuminati Hotties.
